            <a href="/en/dep/bld/Whats-new/Speeches-and-articles/minister/barne_og_likestillingsminister_ramin_osm/2007/Creating-a-safe-environment-for-children.html?id=488526" class="ISI_IGNORE">
                <img src="/Upload/BLD/Ingresssbilder/barn_og_ungdom_deltagelse_og_inflytelse_150x113.jpg" alt="barn og ungdom deltagelse og inflytelse
barn og ungdom deltagelse og inflytelse" class="ArticleImg" />
            </a>
            <div class="ArticleImgContent">
                <h2>
                    <a href="/en/dep/bld/Whats-new/Speeches-and-articles/minister/barne_og_likestillingsminister_ramin_osm/2007/Creating-a-safe-environment-for-children.html?id=488526" title="">
                        Creating a safe environment for children
                    </a>
                </h2>
                <h3 class="subDescription" style="display:none"></h3>
                <p class="ArticleInfo">[Speech/article, Ministry of Children, Equality and Social Inclusion, 05.11.2007]</p>
                <p>Unfortunately, children and young people with behavioural problems often find themselves outside of local support structures. These children are socially stigmatized, and often face defeat after defeat. It is about time we recognize that these children represent far more than their negative behaviour. They are people with hopes, dreams, sorrows and longings.</p>
                
                
                <p>
                    
                    
                </p>
                <span id="ctl00_FullRegion_CenterAndRightRegion_CenterRegion_SubjectManager_wp595570488_wp1872782628_lstSearchResult_lstUniversal_ctl09_Label1"></span>                 
